            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "content": "```python\nchannels = get_channels()\nif len(channels) == 0:\n    raise ValueError(\"No channels found.\")\n\nall_users = set()\nmessage_counts = {}\n\nfor channel in channels:\n    channel_users = get_users_in_channel(channel)\n    all_users = all_users | set(channel_users)\n\n    messages = read_channel_messages(channel)\n    for message in messages:\n        sender = message.sender\n        all_users = all_users | set([sender])\n        message_counts[sender] = message_counts.get(sender, 0) + 1\n\nif len(all_users) == 0:\n    raise ValueError(\"No users found.\")\n\nranked_users = sorted([(-message_counts.get(user, 0), user.lower(), user) for user in all_users])\n\nfor rank_index, ranked_user in enumerate(ranked_users):\n    user = ranked_user[2]\n    rank = rank_index + 1\n    body = \"Congrats on being the {}-th most active user!\".format(rank)\n    send_direct_message(user, body)\n\nprint([(ranked_user[2], -ranked_user[0]) for ranked_user in ranked_users])\n```"
